OL,3,C'Truly a horror story': Bridgerton-
OL,4,Cthemed ball goes viral for wrong
OL,5,Creasons
OL,7,FThe themed event in Detroit was
OL,8,Fdescribed by fans as a 'horror story'
OL,9,Fafter being served uncooked food and
OL,10,Ffar from regal entertainment, as David
OL,11,FHarper reports.
OL,13,FAttendees of a Bridgerton-themed ball
OL,14,Fare demanding a refund after promises
OL,15,Fto be transported into a fantasy scene
OL,16,Fwith live music and elegant backdrops
OL,17,Fdid not live up to royal expectations.
OL,19,FInstead, ball goers got paper
OL,20,Fdecorations, a solo violinist and pole
OL,21,Fdancing.
