OL,3,C'Truly a horror story': Bridgerton-
OL,4,Cthemed ball goes viral for wrong
OL,5,Creasons
OL,7,FAbout 3000 fans of the hit TV show had
OL,8,Fspent between $150 and $1000 to attend
OL,9,Fthe event organised by Uncle N Me LLC
OL,10,Fin Detroit on Sunday.
OL,12,FFor Newlywed Pedro Soto, it was meant
OL,13,Fto be a celebration with his wife of
OL,14,Ftheir elopement the day before.
OL,16,FHe said their ticket also promised an
OL,17,Forchestra, food, a bar and ample
OL,18,Fseating to enjoy the ball.
OL,20,F"What we really got was... Kool-Aid
OL,21,Ffrom a bottle, no bar," Koto said.
