OL,7,FNita Morton is one of many attendees
OL,8,Ftaking to social media calling the
OL,9,Fevent "a scam", and demanding a refund
OL,10,Ffrom the company behind the event.
OL,12,F"Doesn't this look like something your
OL,13,Fcousin had at her baby shower that
OL,14,Fthey ran real quick to Family Dollar
OL,15,Fto get?," she said on TikTok.
OL,17,F"People spent hundreds of dollars, not
OL,18,Fjust on their tickets, but on upkeep
OL,19,Fand making sure they look presentable
OL,20,Ffor this ball themselves."
